node.text: Interested in a career where you can be your own boss and entrepreneur? Well, I have an exciting opportunity for you! I spent the day with some of @bhhscalifornia’s top agents learning all about what it takes to become a real estate agent in Southern California. We visited two of their most luxurious listings—and now all Hannah hears me talk about is when we are building our own home sauna. Check out how I spent my day and check my stories for more info on how you can become your own boss, getting out of the 9-5 office life and into some of the best million dollar listings. Shout out to @paigesellssandiego @blumenfeldgroup @patcairnx for showing me the ropes of agent life!

node.text: What to do on weekends during #DryJanuary? Well, I’m here to tell you there’s nothing like cozying up on the couch and reading some really terrible, mean tweets about yourself. The #VizerGames are now live! Join my team and use your exercise to give back + compete against the other teams like @mike_johnson or @hannahg11 to see who can donate the most meals 💪 

When you download @vizerapp just enter TEAMGREENS to join @8greens and I 🥦

The games begin today, 7/23, and end on 8/8. The team with the most meal donations wins! Tag a friend you want to compete with! 

How to Join:

Show your support and join a team by entering their team code in-app. On the home screen, click "Join Corporate Challenge", then enter the team code. Once you join a team, you can't switch teams.

node.text:
Work from home is here to stay, and businesses all over the country have had to adapt. @dellsmallbiz has been crucial in helping my team at Vizer navigate the new WFH norm!
 
I’ve had to find a way to stay productive and proactive about growing our platform and accomplishing our social impact goals all the while trying to stay fit! The struggles as a founder seem to be forever changing, but it’s been great to have a partner like Dell Technologies to help us conquer any challenges that come our way!
 
I can’t wait to see what we accomplish with Dell moving forward! 
 
#Ad #StopatNothing #SmallBizJourney #ShareYourStory #Windows10Pro
